6	/// Parse a `--pin` value (comma-separated list with optional ranges) into
7	/// an ordered vector of logical CPU IDs. Accepts forms like `"0,1"`,
8	/// `"0-11"`, `"0,3-5,7"`. Duplicates are preserved in the given order so
