format!("{sign}{int_commas}{frac_part}")
```

Trade-off in plain terms: five lines instead of one, but both outcomes are now explicit, the failure case carries its own explanation instead of an `// OK:` plea, and `inf` renders as `inf` rather than `0`. That's the last `unwrap_or` in the file except the two `top_band_idx` fallbacks, whose defaults are genuinely semantic (mid-rank past the last boundary belongs in the top band).

Description body bullet stays accurate as written. Ready to `vc-x1 push main` on your approval.

